Sentencas: A-site deficient La(Sr)CrO3-delta thin film interconnectors were successfully fabricated on porous La(Sr)MnOx tubes using high deposition rate laser ablation.
Titulo: PREPARATION OF LA(SR)CRO3-DELTA THIN-FILM INTERCONNECTOR BY HIGH DEPOSITION RATE LASER-ABLATION METHOD

Sentencas: The La(Sr)CrO3-delta films obtained by this method are dense and void-free.
Titulo: PREPARATION OF LA(SR)CRO3-DELTA THIN-FILM INTERCONNECTOR BY HIGH DEPOSITION RATE LASER-ABLATION METHOD

Sentencas: The film deposition rate was about 10 mu m/min.
Titulo: PREPARATION OF LA(SR)CRO3-DELTA THIN-FILM INTERCONNECTOR BY HIGH DEPOSITION RATE LASER-ABLATION METHOD

Sentencas: The substrate could easily be masked in order to deposit the films in the desired shape.
Titulo: PREPARATION OF LA(SR)CRO3-DELTA THIN-FILM INTERCONNECTOR BY HIGH DEPOSITION RATE LASER-ABLATION METHOD

Sentencas: The substrate tube was heated at 873-1073 K. As the substrate temperature was much lower than the sintering temperature of the substrate tube, the porous micro-structures of the substrate tube were maintained.
Titulo: PREPARATION OF LA(SR)CRO3-DELTA THIN-FILM INTERCONNECTOR BY HIGH DEPOSITION RATE LASER-ABLATION METHOD

Sentencas: The difference in chemical composition between the film and the target was negligible.
Titulo: PREPARATION OF LA(SR)CRO3-DELTA THIN-FILM INTERCONNECTOR BY HIGH DEPOSITION RATE LASER-ABLATION METHOD
